{"tid":2005134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"別讓陶輝(Rupert Dover)跑了","createTime":"2020-05-07T02:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T06:09:40.000Z","uid":140104,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"279e6cfe0879d75da3bc3d78bfedfdcbca833d7b","tid":2005134,"uid":140104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:04:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反貪污 捉陶輝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nvSuiXu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnvSuiXu.jpg&h=ccb1e845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署昨(2020年5月7日)派出四名人員到碧水新村實地調查，但被拒入屋。至於警務處處長鄧炳強曾租住的豪宅被揭發有僭建，屋宇署確認僭建物至今仍未清拆，正在跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署昨(2020年5月7日)派四名人員實地調查，屋內有人以英語向職員查詢來自哪個機構，職員回覆後，屋內人仍拒絕開門。其後職員在單位外圍觀察及記錄資料，並拍攝現場環境，將卡片放到單位郵箱內後離開。其中一名民政事務總署職員許先生稱，拍門暫無屋主應門。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務總署回應稱，根據牌照處紀錄，事件中的處所未有領取旅館牌照。牌照處在接獲任何懷疑無牌經營旅館的舉報後，會在八個工作天內巡查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/local/20200507/3BKLTIZS6XUBZDMZRX3IVKAUHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2F3BKLTIZS6XUBZDMZRX3IVKAUHA%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=578b7158\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200507%2F3BKLTIZS6XUBZDMZRX3IVKAUHA%2F&h=6c412a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/local/20200507/3BKLTIZS6XUBZDMZRX3IVKAUHA/</a>"},{"pid":"826ebd6e55a59383c64a717d242d371a34f98939","tid":2005134,"uid":220431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"犯法就係犯法!"},{"pid":"40b427ca14c96d2076d4797b0cdffa5e2546e95a","tid":2005134,"uid":45910,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:14:11.000Z","msg":"「我完全唔同意我哋不偏不倚執法」"},{"pid":"e1cde7699a1e516cb9b31576ffe806ef4fab575e","tid":2005134,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:16:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83f657610c7fd742938cd9a0efe920e2b57ae868","tid":2005134,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:30:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa0b72aaa1835cde12a222ff3d7af52010d0778","tid":2005134,"uid":198503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"被拒入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪食撚懵左"},{"pid":"43c37b48df79cfe0cd14f3c3ea28a5120485a7c9","tid":2005134,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:31:53.000Z","msg":"做左咁多違反人權既野<br />\n要一齊追討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbc25359f6e2996ff0481e85320115178579b6f","tid":2005134,"uid":84519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"126bbe201f12acc843abefcfe4b24c2373283dd8","tid":2005134,"uid":204539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3aa0b72aaa1835cde12a222ff3d7af52010d0778","tid":2005134,"uid":198503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:31:28.000Z","msg":"被拒入屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪食撚懵左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"早幾日陶輝仲懵撚盛盛大搖大擺行街<br />\n依家學精咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b378e090c215a6025846a6721ec8a0784d6071c8","tid":2005134,"uid":140104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:20:49.000Z","msg":"地政專員：已派員視察，會不偏不倚跟進<br />\n<br />\n趙燕驊其後澄清，言論並非針對特定官員「劃紅線」，只是考慮到動議內容不符《區議會條例》。西貢地政專員馬漢炎亦回應指，收到投訴後已派員到實地視察，並向持牌人發出警告信勒令改正，若未有改正，將作出進一步行動，不排除會檢控；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而碧水新村61A初步已發現有違法構築物，亦已向持牌人發出警告信，但因未能進入，而未完成實地視察工作，若仍然未能進入視察，將不排除作進一步行動。<br />\n馬漢炎強調地政署會一視同仁、不偏不倚跟進行動。動議獲大部分區議員和議，其後獲得通過。區議會主席鍾錦麟表示會將個案轉交廉政公署及地政總署跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/469479/%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E6%8F%90%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E5%8B%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9F%A5%E9%99%B6%E8%BC%9D%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C-%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F469479%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%258C%2583%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%258F%2590%25E8%2587%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%2599%25B6%25E8%25BC%259D%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%25A6%258F%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25AE%259C-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=d83f0e74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/469479/%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83-%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E6%8F%90%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E5%8B%95%E8%AD%B0%E6%9F%A5%E9%99%B6%E8%BC%9D%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C-%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E9%9B%A2%E5%A0%B4</a>"},{"pid":"cd310a6f3733bddf83778ce93c5bd332962e8556","tid":2005134,"uid":191052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"推到上庭為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cbc51e2d33c42ea27e603cc860842d7617c0e6","tid":2005134,"uid":162103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:22:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d57c76c84ebe53f01d573e3416e6f5ba347c7172","tid":2005134,"uid":2083